---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Blog" description="Blog de ESOFT: artículos sobre software, IA, testing, UX, arquitectura y vida estudiantil.">
  <section class="relative py-10 md:py-16 px-4 overflow-hidden"><div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(ellipse_60%_40%_at_50%_-10%,rgba(21,97,240,0.05),transparent_70%)]"></div>
    <div class="relative max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold break-words mb-4">Blog</h1>
      <p class="text-content-secondary text-base md:text-lg max-w-3xl">
        Artículos, guías y recursos sobre ingeniería de software, inteligencia artificial, testing, UX/UI, cloud, arquitectura y vida estudiantil.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 py-10 md:py-16">
    <div class="text-center">
      <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Próximamente</h2>
      <p class="text-content-muted max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Estamos preparando contenido de alta calidad sobre las disciplinas que enseñamos. Pronto encontrarás aquí artículos sobre:
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3 mt-8">
        <span class="bg-bg-tertiary text-brand px-4 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium">Software Engineering</span>
        <span class="bg-bg-tertiary text-brand px-4 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium">Inteligencia Artificial</span>
        <span class="bg-bg-tertiary text-brand px-4 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium">Testing</span>
        <span class="bg-bg-tertiary text-brand px-4 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium">UX/UI</span>
        <span class="bg-bg-tertiary text-brand px-4 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium">Cloud</span>
        <span class="bg-bg-tertiary text-brand px-4 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium">Arquitectura</span>
        <span class="bg-bg-tertiary text-brand px-4 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium">Vida Estudiantil</span>
        <span class="bg-bg-tertiary text-brand px-4 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium">Empleabilidad</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
